creator: 抢喵
descriptionHtml:
SNAPIT is a real cashback e-commerce platform. Users who fail to snap up a product will get at least a 3% rebate. The more they buy, the more rebates. There is no upper limit. A platform designed for online shopping.
A good tool for making money back. Users can also store goods on the platform for 30 days, reselling them safely, editing the corresponding price and putting them on the platform. Second-hand buyers can buy the goods successfully, and the platform will directly deliver the goods to second-hand buyers
In order to save the delivery time of the original buyer. Goods can also be picked up during storage in the platform warehouse. Direct delivery is required.
descriptionShort: SNAPIT is a real cashback e-commerce platform
